text: <!here|@here> Zara is offering a brown-bag session to show the larger team how they are planning to work in Zeplin. If anybody is interested in attending let me know and I’ll put you on the invite. There will be a webex for calling in remotely and it’s scheduled for 12:30-2 on Friday
There will probably be information that we need to know presented, if you can attend, I greatly encourage it.
